text:
A great stream today. :_ちょうちょ:

Again Rushia-daitenshi demonstrates how many she is going more closer with the audience. :_きゅん:
Also this would help for making Rushia-daitenshi more stronger.

Well... These recent months starting September are the "Returning" months... Can we imagine it? Examples:
— In September returned "Super Mario Maker 2", "Ring Fit Adventure" (Last time due to unexpected), "Minecraft", "Shadow Corridor" and "Animal Crossing" 
— October with "Splatoon 2" and "Super Smash Bros Ultimate"
— November with "GTA 5"

What will be next... It would be time to improve... We don't know yet. :_ハート:
